      Speech
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Committing to safeguarding progress made on the Women, Peace and Security agenda
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Explanation of vote by Ambassador Jonathan Allen, UK Chargé d’Affaires to the UN, following the Security Council vote in connection with Women, Peace and Security</p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
    <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds metadata-column">
        <div class="app-c-publisher-metadata" lang="en">
    <div class="app-c-published-dates " lang="en">
    Published 30 October 2020
</div>

